An all time classic: a stunning Isfahan masterpiece by Grand Master Mohammad Seirafian, a living legend and still as charming as ever at the age of 96. A similar piece is published in his book 📚 
This exceptional beauty, in mint condition, is modelled on traditional Isfahani Kalamkari block printed textiles, recalling Qajar era vogues of the 19the century with a central cypress tree of life and flying cranes.
